hotography-955395-2048x1367.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here are some of the services customs brokers can provide:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ensure your goods meet all international, federal, and provincial import-export requirements. They are responsible for contacting relevant agencies<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Calculate and pay fees to customs authorities for your shipments<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prepare necessary documents in a manner that is fully compliant with all rules and regulations<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Classify your shipments under the proper codes<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Save you money by avoiding extra fees, paperwork errors, and shipment delays<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Improve customs clearance efficiency to maximize your profit<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><b>6 Situations When You Need to Hire a Customs Broker<\/b><b><\/b><\/h3>\n<p><b>1. You\u2019re importing from China to Canada.<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> If you\u2019re planning on importing from China to Canada, there are tons of regulations that need to be followed&#8230;and they can change at any time. That\u2019s why it\u2019s wise to hire a customs broker in this situation. Your customs broker will stay up-to-date on all the requirements so you can have a smooth shipping process and focus on growing your business instead of worrying about customs clearance.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For great tips on importing from China to Canada, click <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/blog\/our-top-tips-for-importing-from-china\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">here<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1937\" src=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/pexels-kai-pilger-547494-1024x684.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" srcset=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/pexels-kai-pilger-547494-scaled.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/pexels-kai-pilger-547494-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/pexels-kai-pilger-547494-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/pexels-kai-pilger-547494-1536x1026.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/pexels-kai-pilger-547494-2048x1368.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>2. You\u2019re importing from Europe. <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Importing from Europe is also a complicated process. You need to stay on top of customs duties and other fees so your profit margin remains secure. It\u2019s much easier if you hire a customs broker who can take care of all the paperwork and calculations for you. Don\u2019t make the mistake of trying to manage your shipments from Europe on your own; you might end up with unexpected fees and costly delays.<\/span><b><\/b><b><\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>3. You want to avoid expensive and time-consuming mistakes with your shipments. <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Customs brokers know customs clearance better than anyone else, which is why they\u2019re perfectly suited to steer clear of extra fees and other costly mistakes. If you try to handle customs clearance on your own, you might make any number of mistakes, including submitting errant paperwork, incorrectly classifying your shipments, miscalculating duties and taxes, and overlooking new regulations. Any of these mistakes could result in paying unexpected fees or having your goods seized by customs.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you want a quote for Canada customs brokerage fees, use our free <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/app.borderbuddy.com\/calculator2\/public\/import?_ga=2.228740827.634383119.1608563287-287345881.1608115915\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Canada customs fees calculator<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. You can also use it to calculate fees for importing goods to the US.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1935\" src=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/siora-photography-hgFY1mZY-Y0-unsplash-1024x673.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/siora-photography-hgFY1mZY-Y0-unsplash-scaled.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/siora-photography-hgFY1mZY-Y0-unsplash-300x197.jpg 300w, https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/siora-photography-hgFY1mZY-Y0-unsplash-768x505.jpg 768w, https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/siora-photography-hgFY1mZY-Y0-unsplash-1536x1009.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/siora-photography-hgFY1mZY-Y0-unsplash-2048x1346.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>4. You don\u2019t have enough time to master the complex rules and regulations of international trade. <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As a business owner, you probably don\u2019t have tons of extra time on your hands to master an entirely new field&#8230;and that\u2019s what it would take to manage customs clearance all on your own. It\u2019s not a matter of reading a few articles online; it\u2019s habitually studying the constantly changing rules and regulations of an industry that\u2019s loaded with jargon. Save yourself the headache and hire a customs broker who already knows all of that stuff.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>5. Your import-export business is just starting out.<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> If your import-export business is brand new, you\u2019re already overwhelmed by selecting products, finding suppliers, and choosing shipment methods. Attempting to manage your own shipments and customs clearance will just add to the stress. Those who are new to the import-export Canada sphere will benefit highly from a veteran customs broker who advises them on all things customs.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Are you ready to start your import-export business? Don\u2019t miss <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/blog\/how-to-start-an-import-export-business\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">this guide<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1934\" src=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/pexels-tirachard-kumtanom-733854-1024x684.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" srcset=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/pexels-tirachard-kumtanom-733854-scaled.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/pexels-tirachard-kumtanom-733854-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/pexels-tirachard-kumtanom-733854-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/pexels-tirachard-kumtanom-733854-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/pexels-tirachard-kumtanom-733854-2048x1367.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>6. You don\u2019t have a customs broker license. <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">According to the Canada Border Services Agency, you must have a customs broker license to pay duties on imported goods. To obtain this license, you must be a Canadian citizen or permanent resident and your corporation must be registered in the province where you will conduct business. You have to go through an application process and indicate you have passed the Customs Brokers Professional Examination as well as pay an annual fee of $600. Sound overwhelming? Just hire a customs broker who\u2019s already licensed to take care of these duties.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you want to hire the best customs broker Canada has to offer, look no further. At <\/span><\/i><b><i>BorderBuddy<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, our goal is to simplify the customs process for you. We offer solutions for businesses of all sizes, so give us a <\/span><\/i><a href=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/contact\/\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">call<\/span><\/i><\/a><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> today.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Whether your import-export business is still in the planning phase or you\u2019ve already sent your first few shipments, you\u2019re probably wondering whether you need to hire a customs broker. Although it\u2019s not legally required to hire a customs clearance broker, there are certain situations when you really should. After all, customs and brokerage is a&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1938,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"_genesis_hide_title":false,"_genesis_hide_breadcrumbs":false,"_genesis_hide_singular_image":false,"_genesis_hide_footer_widgets":false,"_genesis_custom_body_class":"","_genesis_custom_post_class":"","_genesis_layout":"","footnotes":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v22.4 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>When to Hire a Customs Broker &#187; Blog &#187; BorderBuddy<\/title>\n<meta name=\